        <p class="text-sm text-retro-brown leading-relaxed">
          Good tools exist, but they cost $50k+/year. SMBs get spreadsheets.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%# Problem 4 %>
      <div class="card-retro tilt-right">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-retro-brown/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 border-2 border-retro-brown/30">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-retro-brown icon-retro" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
